code: public static LifecyclePolicyMetadata parse(XContentParser parser, String name) {     return PARSER.apply(parser, name). }
public Map<String, String> getHeaders() {     return headers. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj == null) {         return false.     }     if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     LifecyclePolicyMetadata other = (LifecyclePolicyMetadata) obj.     return Objects.equals(policy, other.policy) && Objects.equals(headers, other.headers) && Objects.equals(version, other.version) && Objects.equals(modifiedDate, other.modifiedDate). }
